{"tid":45421,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[建築本是藝術] TATE MODERN","createTime":"2016-12-19T03:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T05:44:57.000Z","uid":13266,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b4c58c26e197f105b9ffa217866ed6c1a7f341","tid":45421,"uid":13266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"某日有事出城，經過 Tate Modern，其實唔知入面有啲咩，我本身又唔鍾意好多所謂「藝術」（尤其係偏好將內容、意義抽空嘅後現代藝術，之前做功課去咗間要俾錢嘅藝術館，行完一圈都唔知睇咗啲咩，好想有得回水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）於是諗住行一圈好快，點知入到去先發現原來佢空間設計非常犀利，行行下行到天黑先捨得走。（不過倫敦三點幾四點開始天黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n佢其中一個特點就係好高、好寬敞，因為佢前身係發電廠，直至2000年正式成為現代藝術館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5585/30890735884_97b58f910a_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5585%2F30890735884_97b58f910a_o.jpg&h=90316314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5588/30890735694_9962aa1b5e_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5588%2F30890735694_9962aa1b5e_o.jpg&h=c2005be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話：佢嘅初代識別設計係有75個版本嘅 logo，為要表現「多面向而萬變不離其宗」；後來今年年中統一咗做一款點陣 logo，但仍然係撲朔迷離，饒有趣味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.creativereview.co.uk/the-tate-logo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creativereview.co.uk%2Fthe-tate-logo%2F&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=74b00d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.creativereview.co.uk/the-tate-logo/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/brandnew/archives/new_logo_and_identity_for_tate_by_north.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.underconsideration.com%2Fbrandnew%2Farchives%2Fnew_logo_and_identity_for_tate_by_north.php&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=041d7d88\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.underconsideration.com/brandnew/archives/new_logo_and_identity_for_tate_by_north.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/brandnew/archives/tate_2016_logo_before_after.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.underconsideration.com%2Fbrandnew%2Farchives%2Ftate_2016_logo_before_after.gif&h=a1fcf1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空間設計採用大量混凝土營造幾何結構，混凝土嘅顏色加上適當嘅燈光相當有質感，幾何建築暗藏好多「引導綫」，令行人有想探索呢座建築物嘅欲望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/295/30890735584_69822896fe_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F295%2F30890735584_69822896fe_o.jpg&h=437ce4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/426/31359326240_dcf581e34d_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F426%2F31359326240_dcf581e34d_o.jpg&h=d77df924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/411/31359324670_3719f96c2b_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F411%2F31359324670_3719f96c2b_o.jpg&h=a14f95a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而燈光亦經細心安排，刻意用重複用光管組合成有層次嘅天頂，光暗有序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/427/31359326620_162c77e918_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F427%2F31359326620_162c77e918_o.jpg&h=b5e355cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/735/31359325890_e7940272f9_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F735%2F31359325890_e7940272f9_o.jpg&h=23faa4c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於由發電廠改造成藝術館：雖然英國嘅官僚令好多服務僵化，可能你都有聽過英國人對職責以外嘅事好懶理，但對於保守嘅政策反而有助保育文化，將舊有嘅嘢轉化成全新、有獨立個性嘅新事物，同時將歷史精神保留落去，喺西方文化逐漸倒退嘅時代算係難能可貴。隨街都係幾百年歷史嘅建築物，而鋪面係現代商店，我唔知咁樣算唔算明智，畢竟有時夾硬將新舊融合係格格不入，但起碼呀，佢無成幢建築拆鬼咗吖？香港個濕鳩政府一味識得「保育」，最後原來係一個又一個行唔通嘅發達大計，香港最有歷史嘅文物拆吓又一幢，拆吓又一幢，香港人真係好可憐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/481/31359325560_c80b3b5dff_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F481%2F31359325560_c80b3b5dff_o.jpg&h=faa40939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/528/31359325310_1fd8628910_k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F528%2F31359325310_1fd8628910_k.jpg&h=63e05688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/415/31359324960_40dc19c1b1_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F415%2F31359324960_40dc19c1b1_o.jpg&h=c90ec1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/325/31359324290_f91a786aa9_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F325%2F31359324290_f91a786aa9_o.jpg&h=fbfd0c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今次遊歷，我發現自己攝影技術真係未到家，好多建築裏面嘅美學我仲係未有能力喺相片上展現出嚟，或者係未睇得夠、行嘅路未夠多，或者係睇嘢未夠仔細。無論如何，知道自己不足之處係進步嘅起點，我會好好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFlickr：<a href=\"http://flickr.com/moses4ever\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fflickr.com%2Fmoses4ever&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b5ce6b23\" target=\"_blank\">flickr.com/moses4ever</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/mr.5willow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmr.5willow&d=6F8V%2FcmdKJwXYAFZaRuzKZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=68e0f8c2\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/mr.5willow</a>"},{"pid":"2445d214881af0c117f1fa21c65d71925b5de60b","tid":45421,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" c